{
    "name":"南开选课系统helper",
    "version":"1.5",
    "manifest_version":2,
    "description":"用于修复chrome浏览器无法登录选课系统的问题，及登录后左边侧栏消失的问题，在选课页面添加课程上课时间地点等信息，并能够计算ABC,BCD,ABCD,ABCDE学分绩，提供通过选课序号查询课程上课时间地点等信息的功能，提供excel版选课手册，由于选课手册一年中有三次更新，请每次选课手册更新后记得更新此扩展。",
    "icons":
    {
        "128":"img/bg.png"
    },
    "permissions": 
    [
        "http://222.30.32.10/*",
        "tabs"
    ],
    "content_scripts":
    [
        {
            "matches":
            [
                "http://222.30.32.10/*"
            ],
            "run_at":"document_start",
            "js":
            [
                "js/content_script.js"
            ]
        }
    ],
    "options_page": "options/options.html",
    "browser_action":
    {
        "default_icon":"img/bg.png",
        "default_popup":"js/popup.html"
    },
    "background": {
      "page": "js/background.html",
      "persistent": true
    },
    "minimum_chrome_version": "12"
}
